name: Tokyo Duotone Illustration Free Set
description:
For 12 years, Streamline has made the biggest icon and illustration sets. We're on a mission to democratize access to great icons and illustrations. Many of the world's best designers like Tobias Van Schneider, Khoi Vinh, personally use Streamline.



Tokyo Duotone is a sweet style, friendly and subtle, with a lot of negative space and a limited range of colors.


Our Figma plugin has 140,000 thoughtfully designed icons, illustrations, elements and emoji.
